<item>
            <title>[LU-9926] sanity-pfl test 10 is failing with &apos;clear root layout&apos; </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9926</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-pfl test_10 is failing with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;sanity-pfl test_10: @@@@@@ FAIL: clear root layout 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the test log on the client, we see&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-pfl test 10: Inherit composite template from root ========================================== 21:29:51 (1503696591)
error on ioctl 0x4008669a for &apos;/mnt/lustre&apos; (3): Cannot send after transport endpoint shutdown
error: setstripe: create striped file &apos;/mnt/lustre&apos; failed: Cannot send after transport endpoint shutdown
 sanity-pfl test_10: @@@@@@ FAIL: clear root layout 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the console log on the client, we see&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;21:30:31:[ 9316.263030] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == sanity-pfl test 10: Inherit composite template from root ========================================== 21:29:51 (1503696591)
21:30:31:[ 9316.301650] LustreError: 1412:0:(dir.c:418:ll_send_mgc_param()) Failed to set parameter: -108
21:30:31:[ 9316.412689] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  sanity-pfl test_10: @@@@@@ FAIL: clear root layout 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This test only runs as part of review-dne. It started failing on August 5, 2017&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for some of the failed tests are at:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/03e61258-79cb-11e7-8e1f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/03e61258-79cb-11e7-8e1f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7c77e61c-7d6b-11e7-a170-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7c77e61c-7d6b-11e7-a170-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
