                            <comment id="222401" author="mdiep" created="Mon, 5 Mar 2018 16:40:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on b2_10&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/b8093b7a-2033-11e8-b046-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/b8093b7a-2033-11e8-b046-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="206845" author="adilger" created="Tue, 29 Aug 2017 17:17:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem here is that the client is not properly connected to the MDS. This is a holdover from test_9() disconnecting from the MDS. There needs to be some checking added to test_9() to ensure that the client is properly connected before finishing the test. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
